      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition. The exterior has significant damage including deep scratches, multiple dents, and paint deterioration across several panels. The interior shows heavy wear with damaged upholstery, scuffed surfaces, and staining. Mechanical systems are functional but show signs of neglect and will likely require attention in the near term.",
